text: The 1889 Navy Midshipmen football team represented the United States Naval Academy during the 1889 college football season. The team compiled a 4–1–1 record and outscored opponents 112 to 42 In the ninth installment of the Johns Hopkins–Navy football rivalry, Navy lost by a 36 to 0 score. The team captain was Albertus Catlin. ==Schedule== ==References== Navy Category:Navy Midshipmen football seasons Navy Midshipmen
